---Sending money through banks--

Customer sender, reciever
Bank boa, chase
Account
Money
Name
CustomerResponse
Phone senderPhone
Number number



Boolean authenticated = sender.loginToBankWebsite (boa, userid, password)
IF authenticated is valid
	boolean response = boa.sendMeMessageToValidateThatRightUser()
	IF response is valid 
		CustomerResponse response = boa.provideRecommendModeOfValidation();
		IF respone.isTextMessage()
			number = senderPhone.receiveCode()
			sender.putTheCodeOnBank(number, boa)
			sender.clickTransferMoney(boa)
			Customer receiver = sender.selectTheReciever(boa)
			Account account = sender.findTheAccountFromWhereFundsNeedToBeTransferred(boa)
			Money money = account.deductMoney();
			receiver.recieveMoney(money)
		ELSE
		
		END
	ELSE
	
	END

ELSE
	boa.displayMessageThatCredentialsAreNotRight()
	Name userId = sender.recollectTheRightUserId()
	sender.loginToBankWebsite(boa, name.getUserId(), password)

END
